 search.  
  
 BeginsdoubleDeref: apply Step. 
 Prem0: case Step(keep).  
 TypingInsertedL: apply Typing0. 
 LookupInsertedL: case TypingInsertedL(keep).  
 TypingInsertedL2: apply Find-type-in-envH to Prem0 TypeOfH LookupInsertedL.  
  
 LookupInsertedL2: case TypingInsertedL2(keep).  
 TypingInsertedV: apply Find-type-in-envH to Prem1 TypeOfH LookupInsertedL2.  
  
 witness EnvH.  
 split.  
 search.  
 backchain Type-state-envs-weakening-H.  
 search.  
  
 BeginsL1: apply Step. 
 Prem0: case Step(keep).  
  
 Beginsunit: apply Step. 
 Prem0: case Step(keep).  
 


